fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 slipped 104.75 points or 0.57% to settle at 18,181.75. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, declined 1.41% to 13.11. ICICI Bank, HDFC Bank and Jubilant FoodWorks were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The May 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 25 May 2023.
